      "content": "thanks. that's a good start. could you add a section on \"Permitted Use\" like I mentioned? specifically we want to cover when it's okay for them to use them, like for emergencies or if a teacher actually wants them to use an app for a lesson. also can you add the section on consequences/disciplinary actions?",
